dal.domain
Interface ContactMethodType

All Known Implementing Classes:
ContactMethodTypeRow
public interface ContactMethodType

Represents a single row of the Contact_Method_Type table.

Because this interface defines the row of a table that is an Enumeration tabletype, it is recommended that this interface not be used for simple reads from the database. Instead, one should use the dal.table.ContactMethodTypeTable.EnumeratedItem class so that a join in the database will not be required for static data.

Some relevant facts about this interface:

  • It represents the data that can be stored and retrieved from the Contact_Method_Type table in the database.
  • It has 3 columns, all of which have getter and setter methods.
